        jTextArea1.setText("WELCOME TO BRITGHTERCOM HOUSING AGENCY APP\n.........................................................................................\nDATA ENTRY\nDuring Data entry on the application, do not leave any field blank. Leaving any filed blank may lead to application termination prematurely. \nEnsure you complete the entry and then close the window after completion or success.\nEnsure the following:\nSTEP 1: Add owner of an apartment first. Remember to specify commission as agreed with owner. This must be FILLED in figures for \nexample 7 or 12. \nSTEP 2: Add an Apartment associated with the owner in step 1.\nSTEP 3: Add a tenant to be associated with a given apartment.\nSTEP 4: Start doing payments entry for every Tenant.\n\nDATA MANAGEMENT \nAll Reports are in PDF format. However, in the next release we will provide an alternative to have the reports in Excel and CSV format.\n\nReports currently available are:\na)Payments Report\nShows all payments made for every customer. It also shows any outstanding arrears for every customer.\n\nb)Apartments Report\nGives a view of all apartments currently being managed by Brightercom agency.  Location of the apartments and the number of rooms for every\napartment. \n\nc)Owners and Commissions Report\nShow the name and account details of every owner where these details are made available. It also gives the total collections per owner and the \ncommission earned from the collections. \n\nd)Tenants Reports\nAssist in viewing all the tenants. Details such as apartment, rent payable every month, date on which the tenant occupied the house. \n\nNOTE:\nAll reports are in PDF therefore adobe Reader must be insatlled on your machine.\nPayments Report and Tenants Report. You must specify Dates in the oder of YYYY-MM-DD. For example 2018-01-01 or 2018-12-31.\nDo not use any other format as any other format will generate errors or blank report.\n\nERRORS\nWhen an error occur during the usa of the application, please shut the application down and restart the application afresh.\nThis will enable reloading of the modules.\n\nPASSWORDS\nDo memorize your username and password. For version 1, Change of password has not been enabled. If you forget your password, just create\na new user though the signup window.\n\nFor Further Help or Functionalities\n_______________________________________\nContact me on : 254763404086/254715404086\nWycliffe. Email:bonkewycliffe@yahoo.com\n_______________________________________\n_______________________________________");
